# SUPPOSE THE AMOUNT OF TIME IT TAKES TO ASSEMBLE A PLASTIC MODULE RANGES FROM 27 TO 39 SECONDS AND THAT ASSEMBLY TIMES ARE UNIFORMLY DISTRIBUTED. DESCRIBE THE DISTRIBUTION . WHAT IS THE PROB THAT A GIVEN ASSEMBLY WILL TAKE BETWEEN 30 AND 35 SECONDS.

# In[12]:


# range = list
# arange = array
U = np.arange(27,40,1)
U


# In[13]:


from scipy.stats import uniform
uniform.mean(loc = 27, scale = 12) 
