# ACCORDING TO THE NATIONAL ASSOCIATION OF INSURANCE COMMISONERS, THE AVERAGE ANNUAL COST FOR AUTMOBILE INSURANCE IN THE UNITED STATES IN A RECENT YEAR WAS $691 . SUPPOSE AUTOMOBILE INSURANCE COST ARE UNIFORMLY DISTRIBUTED IN THE UNITED STATES WITH THE RANGE OF FROM $ 200 TO 1182. WHAT IS THE STANDARD DEVIATION OF THIS UNIFORM DISTRIBUTION.

